ArithFunctionTerm, BinaryStructure, InternalActionLiteral, ListTermImpl, Plan, PlanBodyImpl, Pred, Trigger
public class Structure extends Atom
Represents a structure: a functor with n arguments, e.g.: val(10,x(3)).
